{"tid":775393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那邏輯】3歲囝商場玩梯跌死 家長索償$206萬被鬧爆","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:24:25.000Z","uid":54337,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c7b8b2d408d7d0b300d29642a9d957461d6a14","tid":775393,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"3歲囝商場玩梯跌死 家長索償$206萬被鬧爆<br />\n<br />\n湖北省孝感市一名3歲男童，昨日在當地一個商場的扶手電梯玩耍時，不慎跌倒，從3樓掉到地庫，當場死亡。事發時，男童家長竟然在商場的按摩椅上休息，事後家屬反要求商場賠償180萬元人民幣（約206萬港元），引發網民狂罵，「還好意思去索賠」。<br />\n<br />\n發生意外的是孝感市保麗國際廣場，昨日下午1時許，涉事的3歲男童，由父母、姐姐帶到商場逛街。有目擊者稱，男童家人坐在按摩椅上，但就讓男童獨自一人在3樓上4樓的扶手電梯上玩耍。閉路電視拍到，男童雙手抓着電梯扶手，然後突然從電梯外跌下，一直跌到地庫。<br />\n<br />\n男童家長發現出事，馬上趕到現場，見男童當場死亡，情緒失控、倒地。事後當地街道辦人員介入，協助男童家長與商場協商，家屬向商場要求賠償180萬元。<br />\n<br />\n「商場又不是遊樂場，自己沒看護好，轉眼就是180萬！就好像一邊傷心一邊就把心裏的價位想好了&hellip;&hellip;」。消息傳出後，在網上引發熱議，網民一面倒大罵家長「不負責任」，「監護人自己沒有盡到監護責任，還索賠商城，這簡直就是『巨嬰』的混賬邏輯！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533890472_472c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533890472_472c.jpg&h=db6e3622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26927211fae8f3ffcc07d44f30cba14a7e389a8f","tid":775393,"uid":22422,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"商場收番隻蝗母清潔費就差唔多"},{"pid":"4e8b22600ac5569ad89262efa111849f3a668f82","tid":775393,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6592a733cfa045afa54b86cc658ee4ce7947115a","tid":775393,"uid":77473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"都唔知地價跌幾多添"},{"pid":"c70ba6643644767af2b602bc386c32599eba005e","tid":775393,"uid":26354,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26927211fae8f3ffcc07d44f30cba14a7e389a8f","tid":775393,"uid":22422,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"商場收番隻蝗母清潔費就差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"64e3ba5c8ddc0181af6e7c143c72978a6ee6b300","tid":775393,"uid":99973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"人都死撚左<br />\n班畜牲仲唔撈番筆咩"},{"pid":"3a6bad93089ef810b915e6870efa5ce6900d82cd","tid":775393,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"180萬係點計出黎？<br />\n㸃解唔嗌夠200萬"},{"pid":"b1ccfa56400d1078cac3867118f8290245fcf993","tid":775393,"uid":54066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a6bad93089ef810b915e6870efa5ce6900d82cd","tid":775393,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"180萬係點計出黎？<br />\n㸃解唔嗌夠200萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"街道辦分120萬 . 家屬分60 萬 . 雙贏"},{"pid":"e6dc60d8aa142ebf8202ca6f767b2a500a11ca93","tid":775393,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:59:49.000Z","msg":"索得百幾萬咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那人果然命賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43eb00b44b70a82046d3df8cce1ef26e1ee5e583","tid":775393,"uid":155337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:02:20.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6149d544217c1098d9404a7de1745aef9ef09c5","tid":775393,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"跌入電梯咪有得賠 下次醒目d"},{"pid":"ad4cd3a89b47fce1b1a505bf9a3fad99c1b231e9","tid":775393,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/154017_61f504b3bb672a0e7e5f09f14d0c6967.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F154017_61f504b3bb672a0e7e5f09f14d0c6967.